      "rationale": "A standardized modeling protocol was distributed to all three analyst groups prior to model construction. Boundary conditions, loading definitions, and material assignments were reviewed by an independent senior analyst not involved in model building. Two minor discrepancies identified and corrected before result submission. Gradation 2 achieved."
