      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model appropriate for pre-yield regime; bilinear isotropic hardening used post-yield consistent with Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupon data. Frictionless contact at screw-rod interface validated against sensitivity study (mu = 0 vs. mu = 0.2 produced < 3% QoI difference). Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
