      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa) and yield strength (880 MPa) for Ti-6Al-4V sourced from ASTM F136 and confirmed by tensile coupon testing of same lot material. Geometry inputs derived from CMM measurements of five production screws; mean dimensions used with tolerance sensitivity study. Gradation 3 achieved."
